quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,177,"Mo∆ī∆īere welyande Alla nden wonaali tan fewtugol …ďaŇčnge fu…ónaange maa hiirnaange walla ko lunndii …óum. Ko woni tun mo∆ī∆īere nden fof ko: e …ďen gom…óim…ďe Alla ko Rewetee…óo Gooto, …ďe gom…óini √Īalaande sakkitiinde, e denndaangal Maalaa'ika en, e denndaangal Defte jippii…óe …óen, e denndaangal Annabaa…ďe …ďen ko aldaa e senndindiro; o nafqi kadi jawdi -e hoore himo yi…óindi rer…ói e mayri- joomiraa…ďe …ďadondiral …ďen, e on wondu…óo mo ben mun maayi ado o hellifeede, e …ďen katonjin…ďe, e on tuŇčaraŇčkeejo wayrondir…óo e yim…ďe mun, e …ďen fewtiŇčtee…ďe ballal …ďe haanida e toragol yim…ďe …ďen, e nafqugol jawdi fii rin…óingol daa…óe; e on √Īii…ďnu…óo juulde timminirinde no Alla Yamiriri, o totti asakal wa…ó…óii…óo on, e …ďen hunnay…ďe aadondiral ma…ď…ďe si …ďe haldidaama, e …ďen mu√Ī√Īotoo…ďe baasal e sa…óteende e nawnaare, e …ďen …ďe dogataa ka hare si nde tii…óii. ∆Āen siforii…ďe …óii sifaaji, ko …ďen ngoni goongim…ďe Alla …ďen ka gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe e ka golleeji ma…ď…ďe. Ko …ďen kadi ngoni gom…óu…ďe √Īeemtini kon ko Alla Yamiri …ďe, …ďe wo…ó…óitii ko ko O Ha…ói …ďe."
  2,178,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe Alla jokkitii Nulaa…óo Makko on,farlaama e mo'on ko faati e …ďen waray…ďe wo…ó…ďe hoore tewaare e jaggitere.Ngam leptirgol waru…óo on bone makko on:dimo yo warire sabu dimo,jeyaa…óo wariree sabu jeyaa…óo, deyel kadi wariree sabu deyel.Si waraa…óo on ya'fike ado o timmude,maa waliiyu makko on ya'fanii mo,hino fawii ya'fii…óo on jokkitagol waru…óo on ka tottirgol diya no mo∆ī∆īiri wanaa lorra e maŇčti.No fawii kadi waru…óo on tottirgol diya on no mo∆ī∆īiri ko aldaa e saatinugol. Ngol ya'fagol …óon ja…ďa diya on ko hoynaneede immorde e Joomi mo'on, e yurmeende …óee mofte.Kala on jaggitu…óo e waru…óo on …ďaawo ya'fuyee on e ja…ďugol diya on,no woodani mo lepte muusu…óe immorde ka Alla."
  2,179,"No woodani on e kon ko Alla shar'ini immorde e njottiigu, nguurdam wonande on; sabu da…ónugol ∆īii∆īe mo'on, e du√Īugol jaggitiirgol hakkunde mo'on. Ko joomiraa…ďe haqqilaaji …ďen tan gelotoo …óum; …ďen gom…óu…ďe Alla Toowu…óo On …ďe jebbilanii shari'a Makko On …ďe gollitiri Yamirooje Makko."
  2,180,"Farlaama e mo'on si maande maayde nden arii go…ó…óo e mo'on, si tawii himo acci jawle nde o wasiyaŇčtoo jibin…ďe mo …ďen e …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen kon ko shari'a on happi -…óum non wanaa yo fawu tata…ďal jawdi ndin- Wa…óugol …óum ko hannduyee fellitanaa…óo gom…óu…ďe …ďen (huli Alla). Ndee √Īaawoore no woodunoo ado aayeeje ndonndi nden jippaade. Ko nde aayeeje ndoondi …óen jippinoo …óe …ďaŇčngini …ďen ronoo…ďe maay…óo on e yeru ko …ďe ronata."
  2,181,"Kala on waylitir…óo wasiyee on …ďeydugol maa ustugol walla ha…óugol …ďaawo nde o anndi fii makko, pellet bakkaatu …óum on ko e …ďen waylitu…ďe fawii wanaa e wasiyanaa…óo on. Allah ko Nanoowo yeewtereeji jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, Anndu…óo golleeji ma…ď…ďe …óin. Huunde laawotaako Mo e fiyakuuje ma…ď…ďe …óin."